<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.3.11">
<l>iraikkuṅ karuṅkaṭal vaṇṇaṉ kaṇṇa pirāṉṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>viraikkoḷ poḻilkuru kūrccaṭa kōpaṉ coṉṉa</l>
<l>niraikkoḷan tāti yōrā yirattu ḷippattu</l>
<l>muraikkaval lārkku vaikunta mākuntam mūrellām</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For those able to recite</l>
<l>these ten among the thousand of stringed Antāti,</l>
<l>composed by Caṭakōpaṉ from Kurukūr with scented groves,</l>
<l>on lord Kaṇṇaṉ, him with the colour of roaring the black ocean,</l>
	<l>Vaikuntam will be all their villages.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
